    {
      "id": "PopularPost353342",
      "post_content": "This isn't on the same level as [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) or [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt). Right now in Standard we have devotion decks running around with [Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx) and [Mutavault](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mutavault) with no sufficient answer. Literally *nobody* runs [Demolish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Demolish) in their sideboard, not even mono-red.  \n  \nR/G destruction builds that blow up turn 1 land drops waste two turns accelerating to a non-game-ending removal spell. Plenty of defenses and answers are available for cheaper, the most obvious being not to keep a 1-land hand.  \n  \nIf you reduce SR to non-basic, you make it ineffective against land auras like [Chained to the Rocks](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chained to the Rocks) and [Underworld Connections](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Underworld Connections). Reddening the casting cost only punishes fair multi-color decks who need an answer to busted lands. Without a suite of land frustration available this card is entirely fair and deserves a reprint.",
      "posted_by": "DoorDie",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost353342\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">This isn't on the same level as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Counterspell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell\">Counterspell</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>. Right now in Standard we have devotion decks running around with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx\">Nykthos, Shrine to Nyx</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mutavault\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mutavault\">Mutavault</a> with no sufficient answer. Literally <i>nobody</i> runs <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Demolish\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Demolish\">Demolish</a> in their sideboard, not even mono-red.<br/><br/>R/G destruction builds that blow up turn 1 land drops waste two turns accelerating to a non-game-ending removal spell. Plenty of defenses and answers are available for cheaper, the most obvious being not to keep a 1-land hand.<br/><br/>If you reduce SR to non-basic, you make it ineffective against land auras like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chained to the Rocks\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chained to the Rocks\">Chained to the Rocks</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Underworld Connections\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Underworld Connections\">Underworld Connections</a>. Reddening the casting cost only punishes fair multi-color decks who need an answer to busted lands. Without a suite of land frustration available this card is entirely fair and deserves a reprint.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '353342'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy103618\">DoorDie</span>\r\n                                (2/3/2014 5:26:24 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
